00:06:29,550 --> 00:06:37,958
The purpose of this procedure is to provide member of public school committee members, especially new members, with the knowledge of how to request an ad hoc report.

109
00:06:38,999 --> 00:06:39,499
created.

110
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:45,023
Ad hoc reports can require substantial work by the district staff that will create the report.

111
00:06:45,283 --> 00:06:53,649
This procedure is in place to ensure that when the school committee agrees to the creation of such a report that we are able to understand the following.

112
00:06:54,269 --> 00:06:57,151
One, how much work is required to create the report.

113
00:06:57,531 --> 00:07:01,314
