114
00:07:02,567 --> 00:07:05,948
Three, any specific information that is required in the report.

115
00:07:07,128 --> 00:07:14,950
And four, determine if there is an existing report, ad hoc or periodic, that provides the answers to the questions being asked.

116
00:07:15,650 --> 00:07:22,012
It is the responsibility of all school committee members to understand this procedure and members should help each other to ensure compliance.

117
00:07:22,819 --> 00:07:30,203
